quran[118]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,"Ad sɩd-kõtb paam pʋɩɩre."
  23,2,"Bãmb la neb nins sẽn be pʋʋsgã pʋgẽ n yõkd b mensã (n zoet Wẽndã)."
  23,3,"Bãmb la neb nins me sẽn zoet n zãag gom-yaare."
  23,4,"Bãmb rãmb me la sẽn yãkd zakã."
  23,5,"Bãmb me la sẽn gũusd b tao wã ( n yit yoobo)."
  23,6,"Rẽnda b pagbẽ maa b yemb-pogsẽ, ad zĩ-kãngã, b pa sãbs-d-b ye."
  23,7,"La ned ning sẽn bao-a woto loogr poorẽ, ad bãmb rãmb la maan-n-zʋʋg rãmba."
  23,8,"(Sɩd-kõtbã) la neb nins sẽn gũusd b boablã la b pʋlengo."
  23,9,"La bãmb me la neb nins sẽn gũusd b pʋʋsgã."
  23,10,"Ad yaa bãmb rãmb la faad rɩkdba."
  23,11,"Bãmb n na n rɩk arzãn na-tẽngã faado, b na n duuma a pʋgẽ."
  23,12,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd naana ninsɑɑlã sẽn tũ ne tãndo."
  23,13,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd maan-a t'a yaa mani n ning-a tɑblg zĩig sẽn yõgne."
  23,14,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ tɩ Tõnd naan mɑni wã t'a yaa zɩ-pelle, rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd naan zɩ pellã t'a legb nem-gilgu, rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd naan nem-gilgã t'a lebg kõbre, rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd sẽgen kõbrã nemdo, rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd maan-a t'a yaa naaneg a to, Wẽnd bark yɩ wagelle sẽn naand t'ɑ nɑɑngã sõmlem yɩɩd nɑngdb buud fãɑ!"
  23,15,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ yãmb yaa kiidba."
  23,16,"Rẽ poorẽ, yikr raarã b na n vʋʋga yãmba."
  23,17,"Ad Tõnd naana saas a yopoe yãmb yĩngrã, la Tõnd pa maan yam yaal-yaal ne D sẽn naanã ye."
  23,18,"Ad Tõnd sika sa-koom saasẽ wã sẽn zemse, la D zĩndg-a tẽn-gãngã zugu, la ad Tõnd tara tõog ne D kɩt t'a looge."
  23,19,"La Tõnd maana ne-a (sa-koomã) pʋto sẽn yi Mak-kεgla la sibi n kõ yãmba, la tɩ-biis wʋsg n kõ yãmb, la be a pʋgẽ yãmb sẽn rɩte."
  23,20,"La tɩɩgã (zaytʋʋn) sẽn tobd Sĩinɑɑ'ɑ tãngẽ wã, sẽn tar kaam la zẽed (sẽn tar n ninged rɩɩb) n rɩtẽ."
  23,21,"Lɑ ɑd tags-n-gesr be ne yãmb rũmsã pʋgẽ: Tõnd yũnugda yãmb ne bũmb ning sẽn be b pʋsẽ wã, la y tar-b n maand nafa wʋsg la y rɩt a pʋgẽ."
  23,22,"La b poyã zutu, la koomẽ kogendã zut la b rɩkd yãmb n kẽnda."
  23,23,"Ad Tõnd tʋmsa a Nuuh n tʋg a nebẽ wã, t'a yeele:"" Yaa yãmb ɑ mam neba! tũ-y Wẽnde, yãmb pa tar soab zẽng sẽn pa Yẽnda ye, rẽ yĩnga, yãmb pa na n zoe-A?"""
  23,24,"La a nebã kug-zĩidb nins sẽn kɩflã yeele: ""yãoã pa bõn-zẽng rẽnda ned wala yãmb bala, a ratame n yɩɩg a meng yãmb zugu; Wẽnd sã n da ratẽ, A rag n na sik Malεk-rãmba; tõnd pa wʋm wãnde tõnd saam-rãmb sẽn loogɑ nengẽ ye''"
  23,25,"A ka baa fʋɩ, ad yaa gãeemd n tar-a, gũus-y-yã-a hal n tɩ tãag wakat ning ɑ yellã sẽn nɑ n vẽngã""."
  23,26,"A yeelame: ""yaa m Soaba! Song maam ne b sẽn yags maam-a""."
  23,27,"Tɩ Tõnd na n tʋm wahɩ tɩ kẽng a nengẽ: ""maan koglg ne Tõnd gũusg la Tõnd wahɩ. Tõnd saglgã tɩ b hɑlkbã sã n wa wɑ tɩ yɩgrã fuug (ne koom) bɩ f kẽes koglgã pʋgẽ yiib-yiibu (yãang la raoogo) la fo zakã nebã, rẽnda ned ning (naongã) koεεg sẽn reng taoore ɑ soɑb zugu, la ra gom ne Maam neb nins sẽn wẽg b mensã yell ye, ad b na n bõrame."
  23,28,"La fo sã n kẽ (koglgã pugẽ) n zĩnd n sε la neb nins sẽn naag foom koglgã pʋgã, bɩ f yeele: ""pẽgr be ne Naab ning sẽn põsg-a tõnd n yi nin-wẽnsã""."
  23,29,"La yeele: ""yaa m Soaba! sik maam bark sigb zĩiga, Foom n yɩɩd neer ne sãan reegre''."
  23,30,"Ad tagmas bee woto pʋga. La Tõnd me ra yɩɩme n na n zarb-b n gese."
  23,31,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ, Tõnd naana zãma zẽmse."
  23,32,"N tʋms b nengẽ Tẽn-tʋʋm-rãmbã, sẽn yi bãmb nengẽ, n yeel-ba:"" tũ-y Wẽnde, ad yãmb pa tar soab zẽng sẽn pa Yẽ ye, rẽ yĩnga yãmb pa zoet Wẽnd la?"""
  23,33,"La a nebã kug-zĩidb nins sẽn kɩfl la b yags Yaoolem raar sεkã, Tõnd sẽn lok-b rãmb neemã dũni kaanẽ wã yeelame: ""yãoã pa bõn-zẽng rẽnda ned wala yãmb bala, a rɩta yãmb sẽn rɩt bũmb ningã la a yũud yãmb sẽn yũudã.''"
  23,34,"La tɩ yãmb sã n tũ ned sẽn wõnd yãmba, rẽnda yaa yãmb la bõndba."
  23,35,"Rẽ yĩnga, a pʋlemda yãmba tɩ yãmb sã n ki n lebg tom la kõaba, b na n leb n yiisa yãmba [y yaadẽ wã]?"
  23,36,"Ad woto zãra, ad woto zãra, b sẽn pʋlemd yãmb tɩ nɑ n pɑɑme lɑme wã!"
  23,37,"Ad vʋɩɩm yaa dũni ka bala, tõnd kiidame la d vʋɩ, ad b pa na n yik tõnd ye."
  23,38,"Ad yaa ned sẽn wãag zĩri n rogl Wẽnd bala, la tõnd ka na n kõ-a sɩd ye"
  23,39,"A yeelame: ""yaa m Soaba! Song maam ne b sẽn yags maam-a""."
  23,40,"Tɩ [Wẽnd] yeele:""yi bilfu, b na wa n maan mimsa""."
  23,41,"Tɩ Tõnd na n yõk-b ne tãsg ne sɩda, n maan-b tɩ b kʋɩ n sobge; rẽnd halkr be ne wẽg-m-mens rãmba."
  23,42,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ, Tõnd naana zãma zẽmse."
  23,43,"Zãma pa tõe n reng a wakato, a leb n pa tõe n yaoolg-a me."
  23,44,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ Tõnd tʋmsa D Tẽn-tʋʋmbã n tunug-b taaba; Tẽn-tʋʋm sẽn wa zãma nengẽ fãa b yagsd-a lame, tɩ Tõnd na n pʋgl sãnda halkr ne taaba, n maan-b tɩ b lebg yẽsgo, rẽnd halkr be ne neb sẽn pa kõt sɩda."
  23,45,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ Tõnd tʋmsa a Musa la a ma-biigɑ ɑ Hɑɑrʋʋnɑ ne Tõnd yel-soalmã la gom-lubdgɑ sẽn yaa vẽenega."
  23,46,"N tʋg a Fɩr-aoon ne a kug-zĩidbã nengẽ tɩ b maan waoog-n-menga. Ad b ra yɩɩme n yaa zẽk-n-mens rãmba."
  23,47,"La b yeel yã: ""rẽ yĩnga tõnd nɑ kõ-sɩd ne neb a yiib sẽn yɑɑ wɑ tõndo, tɩ b yiibã nebã yaa tõnd yembse""."
  23,48,"Tɩ b yags b yiibã, n yɩ neb nins sẽn halk-bã."
  23,49,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd kõo a Musa Gafã, tɩ raar ninga b na kãndge."
  23,50,"La Tõnd maana a Maryam biigã la a ma wã tɩ yaa yel-solemde, la Tõnd peeg b yiibã n kẽng zĩ-zẽkdgẽ sẽn yaa tabendg zĩig la ko-nini."
  23,51,"Yãmb ɑ Tẽn-tʋʋmba! Rɩ-y rɩ-yɩlmã sẽn yaa halaal rɩɩbo, la y maan tʋʋm-sõma, ad Mam mii yãmb sẽn maand bũmb ninsã wã."
  23,52,"Ad yãmb zãma-kãngã yaa zãma a yembre, la yaa Maam la yãmb Soabã, bɩ y zoe Maam."
  23,53,"Tɩ b wãm-rãmbɑ wɑ welg taaba, tɩ zãma fãa kɩdemd ne sẽn be a nengẽ wã."
  23,54,"Bɩ f bas-bɑ b menengã zug hal n tɩ tãag wakato."
  23,55,"Rẽ yĩnga bãmb tẽedame tɩ Tõnd sẽn kõt bãmb sẽn yaa arzεk la koambã,"
  23,56,"B tẽedɑme tɩ Tõnd kõonɑ D yãgdame n kõt bãmb yel-sõma bãmb sẽn tog ne la? Ka woto ye, ad b pa mi ye."
  23,57,"Ad neb nins sẽn yaeesd b Soabã,"
  23,58,"La neb nins sẽn kõt sɩd ne b Soabã Aaya-rãmbã,"
  23,59,"La neb nins sẽn pa maan lagem-n-taar ne b Soabã,"
  23,60,"La neb nins sẽn yãkd Tõnd sẽn pʋɩ n kõ-bã pʋgẽ n kõtẽ tɩ b sũyã yaeesdẽ tɩ b na n wa leba b Soabã nengẽ."
  23,61,"Ad yaa bãmb rãmb la sẽn yãgd ne yel-sõmã, yaa bãmb n põsd taab ne-a."
  23,62,"Lɑ Tõnd pa rogend ned rẽnda a sẽn tõe, la Gaf n be Tõnd nengẽ n yet sɩda, la b pa na n wẽg-b ye."
  23,63,"Pa woto ye, bãmbã sũyẽ bee yɑm-yɑɑl-yɑɑl pʋgẽ ne yã wã (alKʋrãanã), la b tara tʋʋm-wẽn a taab me n tʋmdẽ."
  23,64,"Hal tɩ Tõnd sã n wa yõk b wʋm-noogã rãmbɑ ne sɩbge lɑ bãmb sẽn kelemde n baood sõngre."
  23,65,"Ra kelem-y rũndã ye, ad y ka na n paam sõngr ye n põsg Tõnde ye."
  23,66,"Ad Mam Aaya-rãmbã rag n yɩɩme n karemd yãmb nengẽ tɩ yãmb rag n yɩ n tard n lebd poorẽ."
  23,67,"Ne waoog-m-meng ne y goɑmã n yit Alkʋrãanã n paoogd-a y sõsg pʋsẽ."
  23,68,"Rẽ yĩnga bãmb pa tagsd (Kʋrãanã) koees n getẽ la? Bɩ waa bãmb nengẽ bũmb ning sẽn pa wa b saam-rãmb nins sẽn reng taoorã nengẽ?"
  23,69,"Bɩ b pa bãng b Tẽn-tʋʋmã, n wa tɩ sek b na n kɩɩs-a?"
  23,70,"Bɩ b yetame t'a yaa gãeenga? ""ka woto ye, ad a waa ne sɩda, la ad bãmbã wʋsg fãa kisa sɩdã''."
  23,71,"Lɑ ɑd sɩdã sã n ra tũuda bãmbã yõyã yamleoogo, saasã la tẽngã la sẽn be bãmbã pʋgẽ wã rag n na sãame, la ad Tõnd wa n kõo bãmba b tẽegr toagsgã, tɩ bãmb yaool n balldẽ n yit tẽegrã."
  23,72,"Bɩ fo sokd-b-la (taasgã) keoore? Ad fo Soabã keoor n yɩɩd sõmblem, la ad Yẽnd n yɩɩd pʋɩtbã ne sõmblem."
  23,73,"Lɑ ɑd fo boond-b lame n tʋgd so-tɩrg zugu."
  23,74,"La ad neb nins sẽn pa kõt sɩd ne yaoolem raarã, b baoodame n na n golem sorã."
  23,75,"Lɑ la tɩ Tõnd sã n rag n yols-b lame la D zẽk keelem ning sẽn be b zugã n bɑs-bɑ, b na kel n duum b kedgrã zug n tuumdẽ."
  23,76,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd gãd-b-la ne sɩbgre, la b pa sɩk b mensã ne b Soabã ye, b leb n pa bõos-A me."
  23,77,"Hal tɩ Tõnd wa pak rag-noor b yĩnga, sẽn yaa sɩbg kεgengɑ lɑ b sẽn be be tɩ b yaa sẽn wãag b tẽebo."
  23,78,"Yaa Yẽnd n naan n kõ yãmbã, tʋbã la ninã, la sũyã, la ad yãmb barkã pʋʋsgã yaa bilfu."
  23,79,"Leb n yaa Yẽnd n sãeeg yãmb tẽng gãngã zugu, la y lebgr pata Yẽ nengẽ."
  23,80,"La yaa Yẽnd n kõt vɩɩm la A kʋʋda, la ad yʋng la wĩndg yõs-taabã bee ne Yẽ, rẽ yĩnga yãmb pa tagsd la?"
  23,81,"Ka woto ye, ad b yeela wala rãeenem rãmbã sẽn yeelã."
  23,82,"B yeelame: ""rẽ yĩngã, tõnd sã n ki n lebg tom la kõaba, b na leb n vʋʋg tõndo?"
  23,83,"Ad b ra pʋlma woto tõnd la d saam-rãmb sẽn reng taoore, ad wãnde ka baa fʋɩ rẽnda rãeenem rãmb zĩri wãasgo."
  23,84,"Yeele: "" ãnd n so tẽngã la (neb) nins sẽn be a pʋgẽ wã tɩ yãmb sã n miimi?"
  23,85,"B na n yeelame :"" yaa Wẽnd n so"", bɩ f yeele:"" yaa bõe yĩng tɩ yãmb pa tagsdẽ?"""
  23,86,"Yeele: ""ãnd n so saas a yopoe wã, la ãnd la Al'ars wagellã Soaba?"""
  23,87,"B na n yeelame :"" yaa Wẽnd n so"", bɩ f yeele:"" yaa bõe yĩng tɩ yãmb pa nɑ n zoet Wẽnde?"""
  23,88,"Yeele:"" ãnd n zãad bũmbã fãa gill naam a nugẽ wã, tɩ b baood sõngr a nengẽ lɑ Yẽ pa baood sõngr ned nengẽ, tɩ y sã n miẽ?"
  23,89,"B na n yeelame tɩ :"" yaa Wẽnd n so"", bɩ f yeele:""yãmb maana a wãn tɩ b wa maan yãmb tɩɩm tɩ y yɑmã yiki?"" (tɩ y pa kõt sɩd ne-A?)"
  23,90,"Pa woto ye, ad Tõnd waa ne sɩd bãmb nengẽ, la ad bãmbã yagda zĩri."
  23,91,"Wẽnd pa tar biig ye, soab zẽng me leb n pa naag-A ye, sã n dɑ beeme n lɑg-Mɑ, ad soab fãa rag n na n rɩka a sẽn naan-a n looge, la b rag n na bao n bugs taaba, yɩlgem be ne Wẽnd n yi b sẽn sɩfdã."
  23,92,"Yel-soaandɩ la yel-netɩ mita, A naam zẽkame n yi b sẽn maand-A lagem-n-taarã."
  23,93,"Yeele:"" yaa m Soabã! Fo sã n wĩnig maam b sẽn pʋlem-b pʋlem wẽng ningã me,"
  23,94,"Yaa m Soabã! ra naag maam ne wẽg-m-mens rãmbã ye."
  23,95,"La ad Tõnd yaa tõogd ne D wĩnig foom Tõnd sẽn pʋlem-bã."
  23,96,"Rɩk sõng n tus bũmb ning sẽn ya wẽnga, ad Tõnd n yɩɩd minim ne b sẽn sɩfdã."
  23,97,"La yeele: yaa m Soabã! m kota Foom tɩ F gũ maam n yi Sʋtãanmbã yuus-yuusã."
  23,98,"Mam kota Foom tɩ b (Sʋtãanbã) ra wa kẽ mam tʋʋmã pʋgẽ ye."
  23,99,"Hal tɩ kũumã sã n wa wa b nin-yembre, a yetame: ""m Soabã! Lebs maam'' (dũni wã zugu)."
  23,100,"Sẽn na yɩl tɩ m paam n maan tʋʋm-sõmd mam sẽn basã pʋgẽ: ka woto ye; ad yaa gomd yẽ sẽn yet bala, tɩ barzah vɩɩm n be yẽ poorẽ wã hal n tɩ tãag yikr raarã."
  23,101,"B sã n wa fʋʋs bargã, rogem ka leb n be sʋk ra-kãng raarã ye, b pa leb n sokd taab ye."
  23,102,"Rẽnd ned ning (tʋʋm-sõng) peesg sẽn zɩsge, yaa bãmb rãmbã la paamdba."
  23,103,"La ned ning (tʋʋm-sõng) peesg sẽn yɩ faaga, ad yaa bãmb rãmbã n bõn b mense, n be Gεhannemã pʋgẽ n yɑɑ duumdba."
  23,104,"Bugmã rɩta b nensã tɩ b noyã yõon n lebg yĩi ɑ pʋgẽ."
  23,105,"""Rẽ yĩngã b rag n pa yɩ n karem Mam Aaya-rãmbã yãmb nengẽ, tɩ yãmb rag n yɩ n yagsdẽ?"""
  23,106,"La b na n yeele: ""d Soabã, tõnd zu-beedã wila tõndo, tɩ d yɩ neb sẽn meneme.'"
  23,107,"D Soabã, yiis tõnd kaanẽ, tɩ d sã n leb n beege, rẽ mosã tõnd n wẽgd d mense."
  23,108,"T'A (Wẽnd) na n yeele: ""sind-y a pʋgẽ la y ra gom ne Mɑɑm ye""."
  23,109,"Ad zãma n rag n be Mam yembsã pʋgẽ n yetdẽ: ""yaa d Soabã! yaaf tõnd la F yols tõndo, ad Foom n yɩɩd yolsdbã fãa ne yolsgo'."
  23,110,"Tɩ yãmb gãd-b ne puglg hal tɩ b wa yĩms yãmb Mam tẽegrã, lɑ yãmb ra yɩ n laad-ba."
  23,111,"Ad Mam na n rol-b-la rũndã, b sẽn maan sugrã yĩnga, ad yaa bãmb la pʋɩɩr paamdba."
  23,112,"Wẽnd yeelɑme: ""yaa yʋʋm a wãn la yãmb zĩnd tẽn-gãngã zugu?"""
  23,113,"La b na n yeele:"" tõnd zĩnda raar a yembre, bɩ yaa raar bogr bala. Bɩ F sok sõtbã'."
  23,114,"Tɩ Wẽnd na n yeele: ""ad yãmb zĩnda bilf bala tɩ sugr mɑɑneg ne tũudmã rɑ yɑɑ nɑnɑ, tɩ y sã n da yɩ n miime'."
  23,115,"Rẽ yĩnga yãmb tẽedame tɩ Tõnd naana yãmb zaalem (wɩsga) tɩ y ka na n lebg n tʋg Tõnd nengẽ?"""
  23,116,"Rẽnd Wẽnd zẽkɑ me n yilge, A yaa Sɩd Naaba, soab zẽng ka be rẽnda Yẽnda, yaa Yẽnd la Al'ars wagellã Naabã."
  23,117,"La ned ning sẽn wa n kot-a soben-zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnde, a pa tik daliil ye, ad a geelg bee a Soabã nengẽ, la ad kɩfr-rãmbã pa na n põs ye."
  23,118,"La yeele: ""yaa m Soaba! yaaf la F yolse, ad Foom n yɩɩd yolsdbã fãa ne yolsg sõmblem."
